    "119321545": {
      "title": "Morita invariance of equivariant and Hopf-cyclic cohomology of module algebras over Hopf algebroids",
      "abstract": "We investigate the equivariant and Hopf-cyclic cohomology of module algebras over Hopf algebroids and derive their Morita invariance. For this, we use the tools developed by McCarthy for $k$-linear categories and subsequently by Kaygun and Khalkhali for a certain class of categories, called as $H$-categories, for a Hopf algebra $H$."
